description:
Cesar Milan challenges the team to build an aquarium at his desert retreat for dogs, which proves a problem when there is no water source for miles around


Celebrity dog trainer Cesar Millan enlists the Fish Tank Kings to build a koi fish pond as the meditative centrepiece for his new retreat for dogs and their owners.

Fish Tank Kings: Fish Tank Kings Meet Cesar
